    <p>Lo­cal singer Don­nie Chan, best known as the voice be­hind the movie sound­track of I Not Stupid (2002), teams up with Shuk Fong, a singer and singing coach who has been per­form­ing since she was seven along­side her mother, a na­tional cham­pion vo­cal­ist. The duo will per­form Can­topop favourites made pop­u­lar by artists such as Sam Hui, Danny Chan and Paula Tsui. Cof­fee Morn­ing & Af­ter­noon Tea is an on­line se­ries by the Es­planade fea­tur­ing English and Chi­nese hits per­formed by vet­eran Sin­ga­pore artists.</p>
    <p>Watch it at bit.ly/2XwtTMX Aug 17, 3pm - Aug 19, 3pm</p>


